metadata.description:
###  Building blocks for Near Social applications.
* Search for common components by name or tag. Initially filtered by `dev` tag.
* Look for curated components grouped by category.

#### Props:
`commonComponentTag` - to filter by a given tag
`curatedComps` - list of components grouped by category.
* `curatedComps` properties: 
  * `category`: Category name
  * `components`: list of components. 
    * `component` properties: `accountId` , `widgetName`

`curatedComps` example:
```
"curatedComps": [
    {
      "category": "Buttons",
      "components": [
        {
          "accountId": "mob.near",
          "widgetName": "CopyButton"
        },
        {
          "accountId": "mob.near",
          "widgetName": "CommentButton"
        },
        {
          "accountId": "rubycop.near",
          "widgetName": "NftVotingButton"
        },
        {
          "accountId": "mob.near",
          "widgetName": "LikeButton"
        },
       {
          "accountId": "mob.near",
          "widgetName": "FollowButton"
        },
        {
          "accountId": "mob.near",
          "widgetName": "NotificationButton"
        },
        {
          "accountId": "mob.near",
          "widgetName": "PokeButton"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "category": "Search",
      "components": [
        {
          "accountId": "mob.near",
          "widgetName": "ComponentSearch"
        },
        {
          "accountId": "mob.near",
          "widgetName": "ComponentSearch.Item"
        },
        {
          "accountId": "manzanal.near",
          "widgetName": "SerchComponent"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "category": "Time and Date",
      "components": [
        {
          "accountId": "mob.near",
          "widgetName": "TimeAgo"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "category": "Compose",
      "components": [
        {
          "accountId": "mob.near",
          "widgetName": "Common.Compose"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
```
